==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reliction
<hw>Re*lic"tion</hw> <pr>(r?-l?k"sh?n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>relictio</ets> a leaving behind.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A
leaving dry; a recession of the sea or other water, leaving dry land;
land left uncovered by such recession.</def>
<rj><au>Burrill.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

